p1.title: Soft Robotic Actuator
p1.content: An actuator engineered for safe, adaptable use around humans in collaborative spaces.

p2.title: Design and Modelling of TorsioSquid
p2.content: An agile, squid-inspired underwater soft robot designed for quiet, efficient movement in shallow, still-water environments, ideal for delicate habitat exploration and minimal disruption to aquatic life.

p3.title: Swing up of Acrobot and Pendubot
p3.content: Controllers designed to swing up and stabilize an underactuated 2-link acrobot and pendubot, enabling smooth and balanced movement.

p4.title: Citywide Smart Waste Management System
p4.content: A smart waste management device designed to tackle garbage disposal challenges in developing nations, improving efficiency and cleanliness in urban areas.

p5.title: Robotic Arm for EV Charging
p5.content: A robotic arm designed to plug chargers into EV sockets under real-world conditions, automating the charging process.
